  "detailed_description": "Your ship is caught in a vortex, survive by moving the ship out of the coming obstacles and achieve the highest possible survival times. On the way you have a helper orb to assist you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447020/extras/975c374685dfd1b20cf645fb1f9cc67a.avif?t=1606237273\" width=640 height=84 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Elegant, minimalistic level design<br></li><li>Challenging, fast paced and fun gameplay<br></li><li>Randomly generated levels<br></li><li>Single-player</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447020/extras/8e11c0cbb789cc56e6030973c3c49bf8.avif?t=1606237273\" width=640 height=84 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to Play</h2><br>The Helper Orb is linked to the mouse pointer, this helps the player escape more easily by anticipating the ship's position.",
